<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>
A <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">Statue base</rs> shaft, complete on all sides (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.51</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.16</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.46</measure>).
</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>
Inscribed on the face; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p>
 ll. 1-9, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.027</measure>; ll. 10-16, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>. Ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΝΗΝ</foreign>, l.2; <foreign lang="grc">ΝΗ</foreign>, l. 3; <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign>, ll.8 (bis), 11; <foreign lang="grc">ΝΤ</foreign>, l. 14.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0260" exact="both" precision="circa" notBefore="0253">A.D. 253-260</date> (<rs type="criteria">content</rs>).</p>
</div>

