</div>

<div type="history" n="text-constituted-from">
<head>Text Constituted From</head>
<p>
Transcriptions (Reynolds, Roueché).</p>
</div>

<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<ab>
<supplied reason="lost">The City <supplied reason="subaudible">put up the statue of</supplied></supplied> Marcus Aurelius Diogenes, the most splendid governor, distinguished, brave, decent, generous, having achieved all virtue, her benefactor; the archons <supplied reason="subaudible">led by</supplied> the most worthy Marcus Venidius Apellas supervised the erection <supplied reason="subaudible">of the monument</supplied>.</ab>
</div>

